<HEADLINE> Iraqi Foreign Minister to Arrive at UN Headquarters </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, March 4 (Xinhua) -- At the invitation of UN
Secretary-General Kofi Annan, Iraqi Foreign minister Mohammed said
Al-Sahaf will arrive at UN Headquarters Sunday to discuss the new
oil-for-food program, UN spokesman Fred Eckhard announced on
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
"The discussions expected to focus on the new distribution plan
