<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, March 4 (Xinhua) -- New French Ambassador to Rwanda,
Jean Claude Brochenin, has confirmed that a commission of the
French parliament has been asked to probe the activities of
French troops during the 1994 genocide.
</P>
<P>
