an intermodal container transport service by five shipping lines.
</P>
<P>
"Each of these consortia has not only allowed the participating
shipping lines to rationalize their activities but has also
contributed to improvements in the quality and frequency of liner
shipping services offered to shippers," the European Commission,
the executive body of the EU, said in a statement. 
