regionally, Virgin Cola will go national, being sold at different
retail outlets throughout the country.
</P>
<P>
The cola will be manufactured and distributed in South Africa
by Virgo Beverages under franchise from the Virgin Cola company,
a new joint venture which has brought together three partners.
