(Group) Co. Ltd., a listed foreign trade company with assets of
2.2 billion yuan, according to an agreement signed by the two
parties.
</P>
<P>
Under the agreement, BOC Shanghai will support Lansheng with
loans, priority services in settlements, information and
consultations. It will also take advantage of its wide network
overseas to assist the trade company's effort to raise funds.
</P>
<P>
