Hangzhou: min. 6 degrees C., max. 15 degrees C., cloudy to
overcast, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Taipei: min. 12 degrees C., max. 19 degrees C., overcast, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 16 degrees C., max. 20 degrees C., overcast to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 16 degrees C., max. 19 degrees C., overcast to
drizzle, clam to gentle breeze. 
