<HEADLINE> Facts &AMP; Figures about Economic and Social Targets for 1998 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 5 (Xinhua) -- According to the government work
report delivered by Premier Li Peng at the First Session of the
Ninth National People's Congress (NPC), which opened here today,
major indices for economic growth and social progress for 1998 are
as follows:
</P>
