Asahi, Yomiuri:
</P>
<P>
-- An advisory panel of Japan's Transport Ministry will propose
deregulating fares for domestic flights starting in January 1999.
</P>
<P>
Nihon Keizai:
</P>
<P>
-- Koichi Kato, Secretary General of Japan's ruling Liberal
Democratic Party, on Wednesday appealed to opposition parties for
concerted efforts on the proposed additional economic stimulus
measures. 
