Dynamo Kiev of Ukraine with a late goal from Filippo Inzaghi for a
1-1 home draw in the first leg of the European Cup quarter-final
in Turin, Italy on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Inzaghi, whose another late goal also salvaged Juventus'
quarter-finals berth in a clash against Manchester United in
December, fired home in the 76th minute when his header was
stopped by goalkeeper Olexander Shovkovsky.
</P>
<P>
Midfielder Andriy Gusin put Dynamo ahead in the 57th minute.
</P>
<P>
Juventus, last year's finalists in European Cup, still had not
find their striking power as Inzaghi and Alessandro Del Piero
missed several chances to change the scoring mark. 
