<HEADLINE> First Session of Ninth NPC Opens </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 5 (Xinhua) -- The First Session of the Ninth
National People's Congress (NPC) opened this morning in the Great
Hall of the People in Beijing.
</P>
<P>
Nearly 3,000 deputies from provinces, autonomous regions,
centrally-administered municipalities, the Hong Kong Special
Administrative Region and the People's Liberation Army attended
the opening meeting.
